attributes.review: hinata runs into da rain, crying. kageyama screams “COME BACK I LOVE YOU”. hinata stops, tears wouldn’t stop coming out of his eyes, “y-y-you love me..?” hinata says with a shocked face. “IVE ALWAYS LOVES YOU! EVER SINCE DA DAY WE MET!” kageyama screams. hinata looks back, tears wouldn’t stop rolling down his face. As much as he didn’t want to cry he couldn’t stop. it was silent for a few seconds, u could only hear the sound of da rain, tip tap tip tap. “i-i-im sorry, i cant do this” hinata says, as he runs off. kageyama runs after him while screaming “WHAT DO U MEAN? HINATA I WANA STAY BY UR SIDE!” hinata was getting colder, it was starting to snow..hinata stopped at the end of the cliff. kageyama was able to catch up. hinata was slowly taking steps towards da end of da cliff. as he got to da last step, he feels arms grab him from behind, giving him a back hug. he falls over and lands on top of kageyama, “y-y-you can’t leave me..i’m nothing without you” kageyama says. the both fell asleep while holding each other in their arms. kageyama wakes up by a girl screaming “KAGEYAMA! HINATA!” he quickly looks up and sees yachi sitting next to them. “what are you guys doing? its so cold!” yachi asks, “i don’t know anymore...” kageyama says. “everyones been looking for you guys! we were all worried sick!” yachi says, “i'm sorry” kageyama says. “its alright, come on the guys are waiting for u in da car, ill give you guys some blankets”, kageyama carries hinata towards da car. once they got home, kageyama placed hinata on da bed. kageyama kissed hinatas forehead and said “I love you..”, “I love you too” says hinata
